  "known_issues": {
    "ppu_sub_scanline": "DISPSTAT HBlank IRQ + HBlank DMA (ppu_status_dma) and BGxX/BGxPD affine (ppu_affine_visual) need a cycle-exact / sub-scanline PPU. They are marked known_fail and excluded from the headline score until the catch-up renderer is verified cycle-accurate.",
    "fuzzarm_armwrestler": "FuzzARM and ARMWrestler report pass/fail by drawing to the framebuffer, not by spinning with R12. There is no headless auto-verdict path today, so they are marked known_fail. To score them: capture a known-good screenshot reference and switch them to screenshot-crc, or rebuild with an mGBA-debug-string-printing harness.",
    "mgba_suite_excluded": "mgba-emu/suite (suite.gba) is an interactive menu-driven ROM with no headless pass/fail signal; deliberately not in the run set. Run it manually for spot checks of timing/IO/BIOS-math/shifter sections.",
